ad%20mentally%20checked%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20these%20places%20are%20incredible%2C%20I%20couldn't%20fully%20appreciate%20them.%20In%20the%20future%2C%20I'd%20like%20to%20prioritize%20traveling%20during%20the%20shoulder%20seasons%20for%20milder%20weather%20and%20fewer%20crowds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBooking%20too%20many%20itineraries%20with%20no%20sea%20days%20meant%20I%20never%20enjoyed%20the%20ships.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20Jill%20Schildhouse%20smiling%20on%20bench%20outdoors%20on%20cruise%20ship%20deck%20of%20Celebrity%20Xcel%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6941ba4f04eda4732f2d9fea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJill%20Schildhouse%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20made%20a%20major%20tactical%20error%20this%20year%3A%20I%20booked%20too%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-avoid-cruises-not-enough-sea-days-frequent-cruiser-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eport-intensive%20itineraries%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20had%20zero%20sea%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20meant%20I%20was%20%26quot%3Bon%26quot%3B%20every%20single%20day%20%E2%80%94%20exploring%2C%20touring%2C%20photographing%20content%2C%20and%20rushing%20back%20on%20board%20just%20in%20time%20to%20shower%20and%20run%20to%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20pace%20isn't%20sustainable%20for%20anyone%2C%20let%20alone%20someone%20who's%20stacking%20cruises%20without%20a%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20real%20loss%20is%20that%20I%20barely%20enjoyed%20the%20ships%20themselves%20and%20rarely%20took%20advantage%20of%20the%20amenities%2C%20such%20as%20swim-up%20bars%2C%20spas%2C%20and%20waterslides%2C%20that%20make%20certain%20vessels%20special.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20hopping%20from%20port%20to%20port%20without%20downtime%2C%20the%20ship%20felt%20like%20just%20a%20floating%20hotel%20rather%20than%20a%20destination%20of%20its%20own.%