.com%2Fred-flags-tell-us-when-chinas-ready-to-invade-taiwan-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChinese%20invasion%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Military%20exercises%20have%20increasingly%20included%20aerial%20drones%20and%20drone%20boats%2C%20and%20experts%20and%20officials%20have%20said%20these%20systems%20would%20be%20key%20assets%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaiwan%2C%20however%2C%20is%20still%20assessing%20the%20overall%20role%20of%20drones%20in%20its%20larger%20defense%20planning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20report%20from%20the%20S.%20Rajaratnam%20School%20of%20International%20Studies%20published%20earlier%20this%20year%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frsis.edu.sg%2Frsis-publication%2Frsis%2Fdrones-over-the-strait-how-taiwans-uav-programme-is-redrawing-cross-strait-red-lines%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrones%20give%20Taiwan%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20subtle%20way%20to%20counter%20China's%20increasingly%20aggressive%20grey%20zone%20tactics%20without%20sparking%20full-blown%20conflict.%20There%20is%20a%20risk%2C%20though%2C%20that%20some%20incursion%20or%20incident%20will%20lead%20to%20escalation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeijing%20has%20already%20reacted%20to%20Taiwan's%20growing%20drone%20efforts%20%E2%80%94%20and%20its%20cooperation%20with%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20by%20expanding%20its%20own%20counter-drone%20training%2C%20%26quot%3Bincluding%20electronic%20warfare%20drills%2C%20swarm-jamming%20exercises%2C%20and%20targeting%20of%20UAV%20%5Buncrewed%20aerial%20vehicle%5D%20command%20centers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%20China%20has%20also%20sanctioned%20some%20US%20defense%20companies%20involved%20in%20supporting%20Taiwan's%20drone%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaiwan-needs-tech-industries-involved-in-drone-push-us-official-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1766411821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22htt