0had%20frayed%20amid%20its%20aggressive%20shift%20toward%20direct-to-consumer%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Hill's%20return%2C%20he%20said%20he's%20been%20mending%20those%20relationships.%20For%20example%2C%20Nike%20is%20back%20on%20Amazon%20and%20has%20struck%20partnerships%20with%20smaller%20retailers%2C%20such%20as%20Urban%20Outfitters%20and%20Aritzia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENike's%20wholesale%20revenues%20increased%208%25%20year%20over%20year%20to%20%247.5%20billion%20during%20its%20most%20recent%20quarter%2C%20which%20ended%20November%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b5e16ef9-8f70-4c95-a19f-8f6de6385f85%5C%22%3EHill%20pulled%20back%20on%20promotions%20and%20raised%20prices%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHill%20said%20that%20Nike%20would%20strive%20to%20provide%20a%20more%20%26quot%3Belevated%26quot%3B%20experience%20for%20consumers%2C%20speaking%20in%20a%20January%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2Fvideos%2Fwatch%2F%25E2%2580%2598nike%25E2%2580%2599s-back%25E2%2580%2599%253A-how-its-new-ceo-plans-to-reassert-the-brand%25E2%2580%2599s-dominance%2F9c5841c6-d480-4a7e-848d-4cd471568564%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Fortune.%20He%20said%20Nike%20had%20become%20%26quot%3Btoo%20promotional%26quot%3B%20on%20its%20own%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20premium%20also%20means%20full%20price%2C%26quot%3B%20Hill%20told%20Fortune.%20%26quot%3BWe'll%20focus%20on%20promotions%20during%20traditional%20retail%20moments%2C%20not%20at%20the%20consistent%20levels%20we%20are%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20in%20March%20that%20Nike%20Digital%2C%20which%20includes%20its%20website%20and%20app%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eran%20zero%20promotions%20in%20North%20America%20in%20January%20and%20February%2C%20down%20from%20over%2030%20during%20the%20same%20months%20in%202024.%20The%20cutback%20on%20promotions%20came%20alongside%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnike-raising-prices-us-expects-1-b